mponents.%20Otherwise%2C%20I%20was%20in%20meetings%20and%20coordinating%20with%20hundreds%20of%20other%20engineers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-engineer-quit-slam-elon-musk-leadership-linkedin-post-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20left%20Tesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20starting%20my%20own%20thing%2C%20and%20later%2C%20in%202021%2C%20I%20launched%20Wynk%2C%20a%20THC%20beverage%20company%2C%20with%20my%20cofounders%20Casey%20Parzych%20and%20Shawn%20Sheehan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20many%20lessons%20with%20me%20from%20Tesla%20%E2%80%94%20including%20three%20that%20I've%20carried%20into%20starting%20my%20own%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2287142afe-4bff-4ae9-b6c1-f6c313f7aa9f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20The%20right%20answer%20is%20usually%20simple%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Tesla%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20the%20right%20answer%20is%20usually%20simple.%20The%20problems%20we%20were%20solving%20were%20incredibly%20complex%2C%20with%20requirements%20ranging%20from%20vehicle%20performance%20to%20crash%20test%20safety%20standards%20to%20energy%20density.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20learned%20that%20any%20complex%20problem%20becomes%20easier%20to%20solve%20if%20you%20break%20it%20into%20parts%20and%20find%20the%20simplest%20solution%20for%20each%20one.%20It%20took%20me%20two%20years%20to%20figure%20that%20out%20at%20Tesla%2C%20but%20I've%20carried%20that%20knowledge%20forward%20ever%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20challenge%20we%20encountered%20with%20Wynk%20was%20getting%20started.%20When%20we%20began%2C%20there%20weren't%20many%20THC%20brands%20at%20all%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20it%20was%20growing%20quickly%20in%20Canada%2C%20where%20it%20was%20federally%20legal.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20in%202021%2C%20you%20needed%20a%20production%20facility%20in%20every%20single%20state%20where%20you%20wanted%20to%20sell.%20Then%2C%20further%20complicating%20it%2C%20you%20needed%20a%20cannabis%20license%20for%20each%20facility.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20came%20up%20with%20a%20simple%20solution.%20We%20decided%20to%20build%20one%20facility%2C%20but%20made%20it%20mobile%20so%20we%20could%20move%20it%20from%20state%20to%20state.%20We%20designed%20an%20entire%20canning%20facility%20on%20a%2053-foot%20tractor-trailer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20rather%20than%20obtaining%20cannabis%20licenses%20ourselves%2C%20we%20partnered%20with%20individuals%20who%20already%20had%20them%20and%20brought%20their%20production%20capability%20to%20them.%20We%20took%20a%20complex%2C%20challenging%20situation%20and%20made%20it%20simple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2234881c72-2e87-4512-9e08-a0ec9ccdc020%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20The%20importance%20of%20quality%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20thing%20I%20learned%20from%20Tesla%20was%20the%20importance%20of%20quality.%20Tesla%20has%20an%20absolute%20obsession%20with%20quality%2C%20meticulously%20testing%20every%20individual%20part%20of%20the%20vehicle%20to%20ensure%20it%20meets%20the%20highest%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20started%20Wynk%2C%20this%20was%20also%20important%20to%20us.%20I%20purchased%20all%20the%20lab%20equipment%20that%20cannabis%20testing%20facilities%20typically%20use%2C%20allowing%20us%20to%20perform%20all%20necessary%20quality%20testing%20in-house%20and%20not%20solely%20rely%20on%20third-party%20labs.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20done%20this%20since%20day%20one%20%E2%80%94%20performing%20all%20of%20our%20own%20internal%20testing%20before%20sending%20anything%20to%20a%20third%20party.%20This%20ensures%20that%20all%20products%20coming%20off%20the%20line%20are%20flawless%20and%20that%20consumers%20receive%20the%20highest-quality%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20tell%20our%20consumers%20that%20Wynk%20has%20five%20milligrams%20of%20THC%2C%20we%20need%20to%20ensure%20it%20stays%20consistent%20throughout%20its%20entire%20shelf%20life.%20To%20achieve%20this%2C%20we%20invested%20heavily%20in%20testing%20equipment%20and%20personnel%20early%20on%20so%20that%20when%20we%20formulated%20the%20product%2C%20it%20was%20guaranteed%20to%20be%20stable%20and%20accurately%20dosed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222f65d380-f3b4-4a97-8d62-2cf3f8d2ae86%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Having%20strong%20talent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20say%20the%20one%20thing%20Tesla%20does%20better%20than%20anybody%20is%20that%20they%20only%20hire%20the%20best%20of%20the%20best.%20We've%20done%20the%20same%20with%20Wynk.%20We've%20hired%20people%20with%20decades%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20alcohol%20space.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20know%20the%20alcohol%20playbook%20and%20how%20you%20should%20market%20alcohol.%20Wynk%20sells%20through%20beer%2C%20wine%2C%20and%20spirits%20distributors%2C%20as%20well%20as%20alcohol-licensed%20retail.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20the%20company%2C%20it's%20always%20about%20investing%20in%20really%20good%20talent%20who%20bring%20new%20ideas%20that%20actually%20make%20sense%20for%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222f27bd2b-c1b6-4c1e-8885-aad92b6edf23%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20thing%20I%20learned%20on%20my%20own%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Tesla%2C%20I%20never%20had%20to%20worry%20about%20building%20teams%20in%20HR%2C%20finance%2C%20legal%2C%20recruiting%2C%20benefits%2C%20and%20all%20the%20other%20foundational%20elements%20required%20for%20starting%20a%20business.%20Tesla%20was%20well-established%2C%20well-staffed%2C%20and%20well-run.%20When%20we%20started%20Wynk%2C%20we%20had%20to%20build%20it%20from%20scratch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turns%20out%20that%20startup%20businesses'%20hardest%20problems%20are%20often%20the%20simple%20things%20that%20every%20business%20has%20already%20figured%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20taught%20me%20how%20to%20solve%20problems%20extremely%20effectively%2C%20even%20under%20immense%20pressure%2C%20and%20also%20how%20to%20work%20within%20a%20large%20set%20of%20disparate%20constraints%2C%20including%20safety%2C%20performance%2C%20regulations%2C%20reliability%2C%20crash%20test%20standards%2C%20design%20for%20manufacturing%2C%20and%20more%2C%20while%20delivering%20an%20exceptional%20final%20product%20for%20consumers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wouldn't%20work%20for%20Tesla%20again%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbnb-ceo-brian-chesky-founder-mode-ai-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebeing%20a%20founder%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20too%20fun.%20But%20I%20am%20extremely%20thankful%20for%20my%20time%20at%20Tesla%20and%20the%20lessons%20learned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-learned-working-tesla-helped-me-start-business-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1762509901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690cf8c17f37aa653f558c76%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-learned-working-tesla-helped-me-start-business-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Angus%20Rittenburg%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Wynk%2C%20a%20THC%20beverage%20company.%20Before%20becoming%20a%20founder%2C%20he%20spent%20two%20years%20working%20full-time%20as%20a%20Tesla%20engineer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Alyshia%20Hull)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A33%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-learned-working-tesla-helped-me-start-business-2025-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22They%20got%20laid%20off%20from%20the%20Microsoft%20country%20club%20and%20dumped%20into%20a%20brutal%20job%20market%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20holding%20a%20card%20board%20box%20with%20the%20Microsoft%20logo%20on%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690cedbf513c94655a3dc087%3Fformat