h%20Hendersen%20took%20a%20different%20approach.%20After%2014%20years%20at%20Microsoft%2C%20Hendersen%2C%20a%20user%20researcher%20in%20the%20company's%20Xbox%20division%2C%20was%20one%20of%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-layoffs-major-round-managers-workers-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E9%2C000%20employees%20laid%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20so%20much%20like%20watching%20a%20car%20wreck%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2045-year-old%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Seattle.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20more%20like%20you%20were%20in%20the%20car%2C%20knowing%20it%20was%20going%20to%20wreck.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20moment%20she%20received%20a%20mysterious%20meeting%20invite%20that%20she%20suspected%20would%20bring%20bad%20news%2C%20she%20began%20laying%20the%20groundwork%20for%20her%20future.%20She%20shared%20a%20message%20internally%20and%20on%20LinkedIn%20to%20tell%20her%20network%20that%20she'd%20been%20laid%20off%20and%20to%20learn%20who%20else%20had%20been%20affected.%20This%20led%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20Discord%20chat%20of%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20affected%20colleagues%2C%20where%20people%20shared%20job%20opportunities%2C%20helped%20each%20other%20prepare%20for%20interviews%2C%20vented%20their%20frustrations%2C%20and%20celebrated%20their%20successes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHendersen%20also%20turned%20to%20her%20network%20to%20find%20openings%20and%20secure%20referrals.%20One%20of%20the%20roles%20recommended%20to%20her%20was%20a%20user%20experience%20researcher%20position%20at%20Meta.%20She%20received%20a%20referral%20and%2C%20in%20late%20August%2C%20a%20job%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHendersen%20credited%20her%20network%20%E2%80%94%20and%20in%20particular%20her%20laid-off%20colleagues%20%E2%80%94%20for%20supporting%20her%20during%20this%20challenging%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20helpful%20to%20have%20the%20support%20of%20other%20people%20who%20are%20goi