e%20because%20the%20holiday%20is%20in%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20Bell's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-taco-bell-chick-fil-a-beverage-strategy-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etarget%20Gen%20Z%20demographic%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20also%20because%20your%20decidedly%20%3Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%20Gen%20Z%20Aunt%20Linda%20would%20absolutely%20murder%20you%20if%20you%20showed%20up%20with%20a%20bright%20green%20pie%20to%20your%20family's%20Thanksgiving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20more%20on%20that%20later.%20Let's%20talk%20pie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThursday%20was%20the%20first%20day%20the%20pie%20was%20available%20in%20stores.%20I%20headed%20over%20to%20my%20local%20Taco%20Bell%20after%20calling%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20was%20in%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20no%20promotional%20signs%20about%20the%20creation%20except%20on%20the%20big%20menu%20screen%20above%20the%20registers.%20I%20entered%20my%20burrito%20order%20on%20the%20self-serve%20kiosk%2C%20but%20couldn't%20find%20the%20pie%20on%20the%20touchscreen%20menu.%20I%20had%20to%20go%20to%20the%20register%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sheepishly%20ask%20a%20real%20human%20for%20the%20pie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22green%20pie%20on%20a%20plate%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690d1652513c94655a3dc851%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Mountain%20Dew%20Baja%20Blast%20pie%20from%20Taco%20Bell.%3Cp%3EKatie%20Notopoulos%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20last%2C%20it%20was%20mine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20brought%20the%20pie%20home%2C%20since%20the%20directions%20said%20to%20thaw%20it%20for%2030%20minutes%20and%20cut%20it%20with%20a%20warm%20knife.%20(The%20pie%20is%20%2419.99%20and%20is%20full-sized%2C%20meant%20for%20sharing.%20It%20can't%20be%20bought%20by%20the%20slice%2C%20and%20of%20course%2C%20is%20available%20on